{"serial": "26036", "department_serial": 23, "code": "OS7178", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Liquid Crystal Optoelectronic Devices", "ch": "液晶光電元件"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Cheng, Ko-Ting"], "ch": ["鄭恪亭"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["5"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "112"}}, {"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "112"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "光電科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Optics and Photonics"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 24, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程將更深入介紹液晶材料在其他光電元件上的應用及相關技術原理，可讓學生能有更多元的修習課程。預期可建立起學生針對液晶相關學術研究以及產業研發之進階能力。此外，將介紹並說明近年來包含學術與產業界的最新且最熱門的研究成果，希望學生在修習該課程後在液晶光電領域有更進一步的認識與瞭解，並藉以呈現國際間最新的研究結果。", "en": "“The contents of the course, provided more and more knowledge about the electro-optical properties of liquid crystals, will give the technology and principle for the applications of liquid crystals and their devices in detail. The students are expected to be trained for improving their ability of researches in academic and industrial fields. Moreover, the latest research results worldwide will also be given in this course. I hope that the students can further understand the field of liquid crystals after they take the course.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 液晶簡介\n2. 穿透式液晶顯示器\n3. 反射式液晶顯示器\n4. 半反半穿式液晶顯示器\n5. 雙/多穩態液晶顯示器\n6. 投影顯示器\n7. 軟性顯示器及電子紙\n8. 3D顯示器簡介\n9. 液晶透鏡\n10. 其他液晶光電元件", "en": "1. Introduction to Liquid Crystals (LCs)\n2. Transmissive LCDs\n3. Reflective LCDs\n4. Transflective LCDs\n5. Bistable/Multistable LCDs\n6. Projection display\n7. Flexible displays and e-papers\n8. Introduction to 3D displays\n9. LC lenses\n10. Other LC electro-optical devices\n11. Polarization convertors"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“““Optics of Liquid Crystal Displays““ Pochi Yeh and Claire Gu, ISBN 0-471-18201-X; WILEY\n““Reflective Liquid Crystal Displays““ Shin-Tson Wu and Deng-Ke Yang, ISBN 0-471-49611-1; WILEY\n““Liquid Crystal Displays““ Ernst Lueder, ISBN 0-471-49029-6; WILEY\n““Fundamentals of Liquid Crystal Devices““ Deng-Ke Yang and Shin-Tson Wu, ISBN 10 0-470-01542-X; WILEY“", "en": "“““Optics of Liquid Crystal Displays““ Pochi Yeh and Claire Gu, ISBN 0-471-18201-X; WILEY\n““Reflective Liquid Crystal Displays““ Shin-Tson Wu and Deng-Ke Yang, ISBN 0-471-49611-1; WILEY\n““Liquid Crystal Displays““ Ernst Lueder, ISBN 0-471-49029-6; WILEY\n““Fundamentals of Liquid Crystal Devices““ Deng-Ke Yang and Shin-Tson Wu, ISBN 10 0-470-01542-X; WILEY“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中考40％; 期末考40％; 點名20％", "en": "Mid-term Examination: 40％; Final Examination: 40％; Attendance: 20％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期四 10:00-11:00", "en": "Thursday 10:00-11:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "光學工程", "en": "光學工程"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知識與科學思辯", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立研究與創新能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "領導能力與團隊合作", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "外語能力與國際視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Professional Knowledge and Scientific Thinking", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Independent Research and Innovation", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Leadership and Team Work", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Attendan